37). How to check reverse PTR record?
cmd: host <ip>, nslookup <ip>, dig -x <ip>

38). umask configuration stored ?
cmd: /etc/profile or /etc/bash.bashrc file, default permissions for file 666, 777(dir)
     666-002 = 664(-rw-rw-r--)
     777-002 = 775(drwxrwxr-x)
